sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>6379,8265/TCP
    participant WorkerPod as Ray Worker Pod<br/>connects to 6379/TCP
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,WorkerPod: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>User credentials
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch notification<br/>RayCluster created
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>HeadPod: Schedule & Start
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>WorkerPod: Schedule & Start
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Services<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>{cluster}-head-svc

    Note over WorkerPod,HeadPod: Flow 2: Worker to Head Communication

    WorkerPod->>HeadPod: Connect to GCS<br/>TCP/6379<br/>No encryption<br/>No auth
    WorkerPod->>HeadPod: Ray Dashboard API<br/>HTTP/8265<br/>No encryption<br/>No auth

    Note over User,WorkerPod: Flow 3: RayJob Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>User credentials
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch notification<br/>RayJob created
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job Submitter Pod<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>HeadPod: Submit job via Dashboard<br/>HTTP/8265<br/>No encryption
    HeadPod->>WorkerPod: Task distribution<br/>TCP/6379<br/>No encryption

    Note over Client,WorkerPod: Flow 4: RayService Serving (ML Inference)

    Client->>Route: POST /predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    Route->>HeadPod: Forward to {cluster}-serve-svc<br/>HTTP/8000<br/>No encryption
    HeadPod-->>Route: Inference result<br/>HTTP/8000
    Route-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 5: Operator Monitoring

    Operator->>Operator: Expose metrics<br/>HTTP/8080/metrics<br/>Prometheus format
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Health checks<br/>HTTP/8081/healthz<br/>HTTP/8081/readyz
